title: Google\Cloud\Domains\V1alpha2\RegisterParameters
name: RegisterParameters
description:

params.name: data

params.name: data.domain_name
params.description: The domain name. Unicode domain names are expressed in Punycode format.

params.name: data.availability
params.description: Indicates whether the domain is available for registration. This value is accurate when obtained by calling RetrieveRegisterParameters, but is approximate when obtained by calling SearchDomains.

params.name: data.supported_privacy
params.description: Contact privacy options that the domain supports.

params.name: data.domain_notices
params.description: Notices about special properties of the domain.

params.name: data.yearly_price
params.description: Price to register or renew the domain for one year.
